Bonnie Franklin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bonnie_Franklin 0 Bonnie Gail Franklin (January 6, 1944 – March 1, 2013) was an American actress, known for her leading role in the television series One Day at a Time (1975–1984). She was nominated for Emmy, Tony and Golden Globe Awards.
